\"Fairy Dust\">Fairy Dust</a> • <a href=\"/Farm_Computer\" title=\"Farm Computer\">Farm Computer</a> • <a href=\"/Hopper\" title=\"Hopper\">Hopper</a> • <a href=\"/Mini-Forge\" title=\"Mini-Forge\">Mini-Forge</a> • <a href=\"/Mini-Jukebox\" title=\"Mini-Jukebox\">Mini-Jukebox</a> • <a href=\"/Mini-Shipping_Bin\" title=\"Mini-Shipping Bin\">Mini-Shipping Bin</a> • <a href=\"/Sewing_Machine\" title=\"Sewing Machine\">Sewing Machine</a> • <a href=\"/Staircase\" title=\"Staircase\">Staircase</a> • <a href=\"/Statue_Of_Blessings\" title=\"Statue Of Blessings\">Statue Of Blessings</a> • <a href=\"/Statue_Of_The_Dwarf_King\" title=\"Statue Of The Dwarf King\">Statue Of The Dwarf King</a> •  <a href=\"/Telephone\" title=\"Telephone\">Telephone</a> • <a href=\"/Tent_Kit\" title=\"Tent Kit\">Tent Kit</a> • <a href=\"/Tools\" title=\"Tools\">Tools</a> • <a href=\"/Workbench\" title=\"Workbench\">Workbench</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414073306\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.077 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.086 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 2585/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 10396/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2129/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2088/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   50.002      1 -total\n 75.35%   37.676      1 Template:Infobox\n 32.12%   16.061      1 Template:Description\n 20.01%   10.005      3 Template:Name\n 10.17%    5.087      1 Template:Quote\n  5.16%    2.582      2 Template:History\n  4.64%    2.320      2 Template:Season\n  3.15%    1.575      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n  3.01%    1.504      2 Template:Version\n  2.33%    1.167      1 Template:NavboxEquipment\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:9706-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414073306 and revision id 185917\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng         = Deluxe Scarecrow\n|source      = [[Crafting]]\n|season      = [[Spring]] • [[Summer]] • [[Fall]]\n|recipe      = Letter after collecting all [[Scarecrow#Rarecrows|rarecrows]]\n|ingredients = {{Name|Wood|50}}{{Name|Iridium Ore|1}}{{Name|Fiber|40}}\n|sellprice   = N/A\n}}\nThe '''Deluxe Scarecrow''' is a craftable [[scarecrow]] that prevents crows from eating a player's crops. The player can obtain the recipe for a Deluxe Scarecrow only after obtaining all 8 [[Scarecrow#Rarecrows|rarecrows]], which will trigger the \"Z.C. Rarecrow Society\" to send the player a letter containing the recipe with a 90.5% probability each night until it is delivered.<ref name=\"mail\" />\n\nThe Deluxe Scarecrow has double the radius (16) of that of a normal scarecrow (8), affecting a total of 888 tiles.\n\n==Letter==\n{{Quote|Dear <player>,<p>Your dedication is truly impressive...</p><p>Only a select few manage to acquire the complete Rarecrow collection!</p>Please accept this blueprint to commemorate your achievement.|The Z.C. Rarecrow Society}}\n\n==Range==\n[[File:Deluxe Scarecrow Range.png|300px|left]]{{Clear}}\n\n==References==\n<references>\n<ref name=\"mail\">See <samp>Farmer::dayupdate</samp> in the game code.</ref>\n</references>\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.4|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.5|Fixed bug where recipe letter would not be sent if there wasn't at least 1 of each rarecrow somewhere on the farm.}}\n\n{{NavboxEquipment}}\n\n[[Category:Craftable items]]\n\n[[de:Deluxe Vogelscheuche]]\n[[es:Espantapájaros de lujo]]\n[[fr:Épouvantail de luxe]]\n[[it:Spaventapasseri deluxe]]\n[[ja:デラックスかかし]]\n[[ko:디럭스 허수아비]]\n[[hu:Luxus madárijesztő]]\n[[pt:Espantalho de Luxo]]\n[[ru:Элитное пугало]]\n[[tr:Büyük Korkuluk]]\n[[zh:豪华稻草人]]"
